entry.content: Day 1 Remove Duplicates from Sorted Array class Solution { public int removeDuplicates(int[] nums) { if(nums.length == 0){ return 0; } int end = 0; for (int i = 1; i < nums.length; i++){ if (nums[end] != nums[i]){ end ++; nums[end] = nums[i]; } } return end+1; } }
